est following the test. The instructions I read suggest that tests should typically run under Native Image by default, which seems to indicate a nativeTest in the workflow after javaTest.\\n\\n**Exploring metadata options**\\n\\nI’m considering if I could add manual metadata reflection for a private method or field. Would that broaden the usability? It seems that this would only apply to the active class. I need to verify if we have the correct metadata syntax. This involves searching through the method entries to see what’s possible. There’s definitely some complexity here, but it could lead to improved functionality!\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0daabe48e56945910169f732d5366081a29914c293bfa40944\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp9zLuNe81JxclT1cPTfAkq2CvpwTxKplpi3n3rV5I9BR8nhecSzem9WryEDNVzy7C7Is6Sl0-sAxzeQC9DVyVIZkhwIvD915lvWcGliwAcfhEq9e3T0DX_xyyW3GBsviXxYU8V6vVdOopTFOE9pS_Bsf2LUQdY49oyqzT0-HM301wcBVRBkvaw5KO8g4zugNPQ-4WjmUfFVI5Ule1swqigaAUieAO3gPACT3YXM32Zaip-Zc2YDjzj2R_WJ4crpi78f1lyQfsKznO5F12Y3vEAKk-7zbzm7lBv6fVkKVa1wrU_Iejcox4rmK8sMU8E77NLV2AG7u8TiUuPsFZSsu9bn6qWNojjEVGqx4_ujK_m1AW_KLsNChAOA9I4_Q00Y9GSGPtIxPq0DrG0Rn2er7sb44eaozLPBjolaa8jkHPpLHCD9dRFinlg_RNuoEl6vRBDwLrvq8T3VzQg0n-NPITFs50cAaJkaD2PxaqYCPp47ozgz4RPW0Rx24o4ByVWBrlkBL_QhhKwawzzkO47PtHB4GqFYfa9ZT4aer0iyQIfXdmwr8L4ftHwb5PDIPb-wWmV-rT1u0-uhTug7Tl-AaKJScZemujamWXFzQ0D87YyCJePVpEiCflKZBq1fU1q6DdOj9tx9GtzLliokEey9bmR61Q37ZROy5UN9JWZQxL2cpO1txwWrPG_2a8t-to67SnwMAlK_42Jz1CULZKc3vCPT2iFt0cWtDX1HAiGZDx1sqZyBQBXrLpbrF17ibVTDwWOqrVFoTFcE7ubCX_qqb2aH65vOnR8mZPLL2b-ZJSMDTGBz2jwfWLwa57Qe0psHqi7rGCu_RVz8yKGtfgIhSEGfSH4-R92E2hPe0RWO6qfDbJFg2rCvZB1FY1WM04fVRxo_7KSGCTgwGLNXU55FVWo4cFBFatq5PguLWSjuXkdM0uSIzZUNj1KjSHMZ0FHsXHx0i3i8iYNeFKg2J-bW_d2Cf6bM9utncRC5b_-hBk-PX8RMbWVr3GDNtKuqvqJjJgdEahDY-7jdbVaohSYF7-kpD8v1hvTxUEVHvM8E_uzATf0q8wYSvgu_A5Irsn1w1TobJ20ve7maGyAfWC6D7VFsFL_oBnid8CGKogTkxNxKxIc9sJqR5_36mA8LY2109wC9MHdL0mMAmOXQROi59XKlJpu6xDwPUl3mEY-V2t-1QLr8hcS6